text:
Hi
I am not able to find 'richpanel' in the marketplace. It is a customer-support tool just like Zendesk. It used to exist in the marketplace. I am not sure whether HubSpot's new marketplace got updated or my product 'richpanel' got de-listed. Can someone help me in getting back to this marketplace.
In your developer account, click App Marketplace > Listings, this will show any listings you have and their status.  (<https://developers.HubSpot.com/docs/api/listing-your-app|more info>)
